## ⚠️ Status: Alpha

Stratim `0.1-alpha` is feature-complete for core book structure:
- ✅ Metadata, sections, inline links, footnotes, formatting
- ⚠️ Lists: content preserved, visual indentation via CSS (planned in beta)
- ⚠️ Nesting `^`/`v`: basic support, full hierarchy in v0.2

**Production use**: Safe for personal/archival conversion.  
**Commercial use**: Requires [Commercial License](LICENSE-COMMERCIAL).